# beyondtrust_workload_credentials_static_secret (Ephemeral Resource)

Ephemeral resource for reading static secrets from BeyondTrust Workload Credentials. Secret values are never stored in Terraform state or plan files.

~> **Important:** Ephemeral resources are available in Terraform 1.10+. Secret values are never stored in Terraform state or plan files.

## Example Usage

{{tffile "examples/ephemeral-resources/beyondtrust_workload_credentials_static_secret/ephemeral-resource.tf"}}

## Schema

### Required

- `name` (String) The name of the secret to read.

### Optional

- `folder` (String) The parent folder path (e.g., `production` or `production/aws`). Leave empty for root level.

### Read-Only

- `value` (Map of String, Sensitive) The secret key-value pairs. Never stored in state.
